'''6-羟基黄酮'''（{{lang-en|6-Hydroxyflavone}}）是一种[[黄酮类化合物|黄酮类化合物]]，是[[细胞色素P450|细胞色素P450]]酶[[CYP2C9|CYP2C9]]的{{le|非竞争性抑制|Non-competitive inhibition}}剂。6-羟基黄酮可在[[黄花假杜鹃|黄花假杜鹃]]（学名：''Barleria prionitis''）的叶子中发现<ref>{{cite book|author=M Daniel|title=Medicinal Plants: Chemistry and Properties|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=5sU6yo1jFxQC&pg=PA78|year=2006|publisher=Science Publishers|isbn=978-1-57808-395-4|page=78|access-date=2021-01-08|archive-date=2022-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220309004706/https://books.google.com/books?id=5sU6yo1jFxQC&pg=PA78}}</ref>，
有可能成为治疗焦虑样障碍的潜在药物<ref>{{citation|doi=10.1016/j.bcp.2009.12.024|pmid=20067772|title=GABAA receptor subtype selectivity underlying anxiolytic effect of 6-hydroxyflavone|journal=Biochemical Pharmacology|volume=79|issue=9|pages=1337–1344|year=2010|last1=Ren|first1=Lihuan|last2=Wang|first2=Feng|last3=Xu|first3=Zhiwen|last4=Chan|first4=Wing Man|last5=Zhao|first5=Cunyou|last6=Xue|first6=Hong}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://en.huatengsci.com/product/6-HYDROXYFLAVONE.html|title=6-HYDROXYFLAVONE {{!}} CAS:6665-83-4 {{!}} Huateng Pharma {{!}} Pharmaceutical chemical reagents, PEG derivatives|website=en.huatengsci.com|access-date=2020-03-27|archive-date=2021-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110093817/http://en.huatengsci.com/product/6-HYDROXYFLAVONE.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。


